						<div class="postbody">[Re, 1 direction scrolling]<br /><br />Maybe next time. I'm very busy these days.<br /><br />Also, you can use the all-direction engine to just go horizontally (keep Y at zero, or in the 2 nametable tall range)...or vertically (keep X zero, ot in the 2 nametable wide range)...with slight modification.<br /><br />And stop calling the &quot;fill the ppu buffer&quot; for the opposite direction, and change the mirroring in the .cfg file, if you want.</div>

					
